We brought Champ's Churros, mo!
Now, eat as much as you want, mo!

rows.label: qst201615_msg0003
rows.name: Well? Have you calmed down a bit?

rows.label: qst201615_msg0004
rows.name:
...Yes, it was very delicious.
Kumarin seems satisfied too...

rows.label: qst201615_msg0005
rows.name: Yes... I feel a little better.

rows.label: qst201615_msg0006
rows.name: Yay! Then, can you sing, mo?

rows.label: qst201615_msg0008
rows.name:
Then let's start the concert, mo! No matter
how good Teetapz's conversational skills are,
the audience is getting impatient, mo.
